
Metrolyrics Scraper is a Java application for searching and scraping lyrics
from metrolyrics.com. The link address to the lyrics of user entered text is
scraped from Google search result of the same user input text as search query.
The lyrics can also be saved offline as text file.

features:
	* easy to find lyrics
	* save as option
	* google search integration provides auto correction for misspellings
	* system clipboard integration
	
Metrolyrics Scraper is an open source project licensed under the MIT License.

Metrolyrics Scraper uses jsoup (http://jsoup.org/) for parsing html.

